    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! If you're looking for a car that's been loved more than my own lawn, you've found it. I\u2019ve spent countless Saturday mornings hand-polishing this beauty, and it truly shows. It\u2019s in such incredible shape that it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every time I get behind the wheel, I can\u2019t help but smile\u2014it\u2019s just that smooth. I\u2019m only letting it go because I need the space for a new project, but I\u2019m looking for a fellow enthusiast who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come by, have a coffee, and let\u2019s get you in the driver\u2019s seat!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
