    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine the golden hour light dancing across the hand-polished curves of this automotive masterpiece. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a time capsule from an era when engineering met art. Sliding into the supple, leather-wrapped cockpit, you\u2019re greeted by the faint scent of heritage and the promise of the open road. Every hum of the engine is a whispered secret from a more elegant time, offering a driving experience so pure it feels like a lost language rediscovered. This vehicle has been curated with a devotion that transcends mere maintenance, standing as a pristine testament to an age of unrivaled style. It is ready to be the crown jewel of your collection and the protagonist of your next great adventure.",
      "price": 44500.0,
